title: Verify that UCIDownloader service is able to sync UCI scores from multiple GCS
custom_summary: Verify that UCIDownloader service is able to sync UCI scores from multiple GCS
custom_steps:
- Configue UCIDownloader subscribe to multiple topics
- Enable UCIDownloader
- Monitor log of topic and GCS UCIDownloader download from.
custom_expected:
- UCIDownloader should be able to subscribe multiple topic
- UCIDownloader should be able to download UCI score file from multiple GCS bucket.
